snippet.title: ONE PUNCH MAN: A HERO NOBODY KNOW – DLC 1 Suiryu
snippet.description:
Stepping in is five-time Super Fight champion, #Suiryu! 


Prepare to unleash a fury of martial arts moves when Suiryu arrives to save the day! #OnePunchMan A Hero Nobody Knows – DLC 1 arrives April 9th, 2020! bandainam.co/OnePunchManPO
